decks.notes: This deck revolves around playing aggressively and disrupting the opponent's game plan. It utilizes cheap spells like Spell Pierce and Counterspell to counter key spells, while also using efficient creatures like Dragon's Rage Channeler, Ragavan, Nimble Pilferer, and Murktide Regent to apply pressure. The deck also has card selection and card advantage tools like Expressive Iteration and Mishra's Bauble. With removal spells like Unholy Heat and Lightning Bolt, it aims to control the board and maintain tempo. The deck has a strong mana base with fetch lands and dual lands to ensure consistency and flexibility in casting spells.

The main concept of this deck is to aggressively deal damage to the opponent as quickly as possible by utilizing low-cost, efficient burn spells and creatures with haste. By consistently attacking the opponent's life total and keeping them on the defensive, the deck aims to close out the game before the opponent can establish their own strategy. The deck focuses on maintaining pressure and forcing the opponent to react, making it difficult for them to stabilize and gain control of the game.
